rComments: His teaching style is to intimidate and scare students into learning the material; he is a very intense lecturer.  But the funniest things I have ever heard during a class come from him.  He knows the material well and his class if very structured.  If you are going to take 403 with him, be sure to take his 300 section.

His lectures are set up nicely in his course packet and he knows what he's talking about.  His handwriting is impossible to read so if you don't keep in lecture you're screwed.  Oh and he doesn't answer questions.  This is a HARD class.  But if you go to lecture, read, and study hard it is totally manageable.

I really liked Prof. Rozskowski.  He really teaches the material so clearly and makes sure students understand it.  He's very weird and the class will be different that any other class you've taken but you come out with a great knowledge of business law.  He's not that hard... just make sure you study and work hard and you will do fine in his class

Despite complaints from other students, Professor Roszkowski is a great professor.  He explains the material very clearly and in a way that will hold your attention. Very thorough, extremely hard, but very worth it.  Aside from helping me do very well on that section on the CPA exam, he gave some good life lessons.

Very interesting class, he really knows his stuff. Not as easy as other ba classes, but at least it's not boring and you really do learn a lot of new and interesting things.  The tests are detailed, but if you study you should do fine
Knows his stuff.  Hardest T/F ever!  Go to class, he takes attedence for e.c.  Scary dude - He could move around during tests silent as a ghost and scare the sh*t out of you!
His handwriting sucks and he won't do anything about it.  Not much of business law is on the CPA exam.  Although, I did well on the tiny part that was on it.  Tax will help more.
Thinks his class is way too important...time very time consuming and unnecessarily difficult
Take a different teacher. The advising office even told me this. He thinks hes hot stuff, but hes not helpful and the tests are hard.

Well, every time you see the guy you start thinking about any bad thing you have ever done and about possible consequences. Material is really clear, his lectures are extremely helpful, as well as a book. EXAMS SUCKS BADLY, many questions and not enough time. Plus no help if you get lost :(
Material was very easy, straight from lectures and book.  Tests really easy.  Very boring though.  Offers no help if needed I noticed.
boring
His tests are extremely difficult. If you do not go to class and take very detailed notes, you will not do well. He flies through material. Test are also very long and VERY detailed.
He was the scariest teacher I've had and the tests were extremely hard
Very clear expectations.  Tests were tough, but lecture was bearable.
